def multiple(x):
    if x % 15 == 0: return "BangBoom"
    if x % 5 == 0: return "Boom"
    if x % 3 == 0: return "Bang"
    return "Miss"

def multiple(x):
    return"BangBoom" if not x % 15 else ("Boom" if not x % 5 else ("Bang" if not x % 3 else "Miss"))

def multiple(x):
    return "{}{}".format("" if x % 3 else "Bang", "" if x % 5 else "Boom") or "Miss"
